549
00:22:38,720 --> 00:22:40,360
Is there anyone to take care of you at home?

550
00:22:40,360 --> 00:22:40,840
I will.

551
00:22:44,240 --> 00:22:45,320
With Doctor Lv,

552
00:22:45,320 --> 00:22:46,440
I won't worry about it anymore.

553
00:22:46,760 --> 00:22:48,720
Doctor Lv, look.

554
00:22:48,720 --> 00:22:49,980
If the head nurse didn't tell me

555
00:22:49,980 --> 00:22:50,730
you're here today,

556
00:22:50,880 --> 00:22:51,960
I wouldn't know about it at all.

557
00:22:51,960 --> 00:22:53,800
Do tell me next time you're here.

558
00:22:53,800 --> 00:22:56,000
Come to me if you need any help.

559
00:22:56,000 --> 00:22:57,840
Go back to work, Dong.

560
00:22:57,840 --> 00:22:58,600
It's not urgent.

561
00:22:58,600 --> 00:22:59,320
Alright.

562
00:22:59,360 --> 00:23:00,080
Madam.

563
00:23:00,120 --> 00:23:01,880
Get some good rest after going back home.

564
00:23:01,880 --> 00:23:02,560
Goodbye, Doctor Lv.

565
00:23:02,560 --> 00:23:03,180
Bye, madam.

566
00:23:03,180 --> 00:23:04,160
Thank you, President Dong.

567
00:23:04,160 --> 00:23:04,950
It's my pleasure.

568
00:23:04,950 --> 00:23:05,600
Bye.

569
00:23:06,280 --> 00:23:07,240
Let's go.

570
00:23:07,880 --> 00:23:08,400
Ms. Bai,

571
00:23:08,400 --> 00:23:10,640
I still think we should tell Xiaoyu

572
00:23:10,640 --> 00:23:11,440
and Xue.

573
00:23:11,760 --> 00:23:13,000
There you go again.

574
00:23:13,240 --> 00:23:14,960
When I say we won't tell them, we won't.

575
00:23:15,640 --> 00:23:18,120
It's not an illness that disables me from 
 taking care of myself.

576
00:23:18,120 --> 00:23:19,440
Listen to me.

577
00:23:19,440 --> 00:23:20,440
Let's go.

578
00:23:20,440 --> 00:23:22,400
Take away the record, madam.

579
00:23:22,400 --> 00:23:23,160
Thanks.

580
00:23:23,880 --> 00:23:24,400
OK.

581
00:23:25,160 --> 00:23:26,160
Thank you, Doctor Li.

582
00:23:26,280 --> 00:23:26,840
Bye.

583
00:23:27,440 --> 00:23:28,080
Bye.

584
00:23:35,200 --> 00:23:36,280
I'm so full.

585
00:23:40,320 --> 00:23:41,800
You lay down the moment you're full.

586
00:23:46,760 --> 00:23:48,640
Let's have some desserts.

587
00:23:50,520 --> 00:23:52,000
There were desserts, and you didn't eat.

588
00:23:52,400 --> 00:23:54,960
I just like desserts made by Cheese.

589
00:23:56,840 --> 00:23:57,760
Yu Songyang.

590
00:23:57,760 --> 00:23:59,800
We're still fixing our relationship.

591
00:23:59,800 --> 00:24:01,720
You'd better behave well.

592
00:24:01,720 --> 00:24:03,720
Otherwise, I will flick you any moment.

593
00:24:03,720 --> 00:24:06,840
Flick, flick, flick.

594
00:24:06,840 --> 00:24:07,840
I'll do as you command.

595
00:24:20,640 --> 00:24:21,760
Hi, granny.

596
00:24:21,760 --> 00:24:23,260
Have you received the strawberries

597
00:24:23,260 --> 00:24:24,000
I sent you?

598
00:24:25,440 --> 00:24:26,440
Are they sweet?

599
00:24:29,000 --> 00:24:30,520
Granny, here's the thing.

600
00:24:30,520 --> 00:24:31,720
I have something to do recently.

601
00:24:31,720 --> 00:24:33,600
I haven't finished it.

602
00:24:33,600 --> 00:24:36,360
So I probably won't have time to visit you.

603
00:24:36,360 --> 00:24:37,920
Be good

604
00:24:39,520 --> 00:24:41,200
and stay together with Doctor Lv.

605
00:24:43,360 --> 00:24:43,880
Alright.

606
00:24:43,880 --> 00:24:44,480
That's it, then.

607
00:24:44,480 --> 00:24:45,480
Bye-bye.

608
00:24:48,160 --> 00:24:49,600
Why are you smiling?

609
00:24:50,600 --> 00:24:51,960
You worry about her so much.

610
00:24:55,800 --> 00:24:58,080
These strawberries are sent by my granddaughter.

611
00:24:58,440 --> 00:25:00,240
She keeps asking if I ate them.

612
00:25:00,600 --> 00:25:01,560
Did you tell her

613
00:25:01,560 --> 00:25:03,160
that you fell hard

614
00:25:03,160 --> 00:25:05,000
just because of these strawberries?

615
00:25:05,240 --> 00:25:06,880
Why would I tell her?

616
00:25:06,880 --> 00:25:08,320
She can't bear the pain for me.

617
00:25:08,840 --> 00:25:09,840
If she comes back,

618
00:25:09,840 --> 00:25:11,320
she will make a fuss.

619
00:25:12,800 --> 00:25:15,080
But I want to bear the pain for you.

620
00:25:15,640 --> 00:25:17,320
Listen,

621
00:25:17,320 --> 00:25:18,600
these days,

622
00:25:18,600 --> 00:25:20,560
you need to come here and cook for me.

623
00:25:21,520 --> 00:25:23,840
I'm not used to eating in restaurants.

624
00:25:23,840 --> 00:25:24,960
Alright.

625
00:25:24,960 --> 00:25:27,760
As long as you want to teach me, I will be here and learn.

626
00:25:29,600 --> 00:25:30,840
The fish is ready.

627
00:25:30,840 --> 00:25:31,960
I'll go.

628
00:25:33,040 --> 00:25:33,960
Slow down.

629
00:25:34,000 --> 00:25:35,920
Don't hurt yourself too.

630
00:25:36,600 --> 00:25:37,560
It's okay.

631
00:25:44,600 --> 00:25:45,560
Did you burn yourself?

632
00:25:50,000 --> 00:25:51,120
You're so clumsy.

633
00:25:51,120 --> 00:25:52,480
Did you burn yourself?

634
00:25:52,480 --> 00:25:53,360
I'm alright.

635
00:25:53,360 --> 00:25:54,560
You burnt yourself.

636
00:25:54,560 --> 00:25:56,080
The more I want to show you,

637
00:25:56,640 --> 00:25:57,960
the worse I perform.

638
00:25:59,520 --> 00:26:00,920
Put it down.

639
00:26:04,520 --> 00:26:06,600
Add the seasoned soy sauce for seafood.

640
00:26:06,960 --> 00:26:07,680
Alright.

641
00:26:11,120 --> 00:26:11,760
Good.

642
00:26:13,000 --> 00:26:14,800
Put the shredded chives

643
00:26:15,320 --> 00:26:16,280
on the fish.

644
00:26:19,640 --> 00:26:20,280
Be quick.

645
00:26:20,280 --> 00:26:21,440
The oil will catch fire.

646
00:26:24,480 --> 00:26:26,640
Turn off the fire.

647
00:26:27,680 --> 00:26:30,320
You can't multitask at all.

648
00:26:30,320 --> 00:26:32,080
It's my first attempt, after all.

649
00:26:32,080 --> 00:26:33,160
Splash the oil.

650
00:26:37,480 --> 00:26:38,480
All of it?

651
00:26:38,480 --> 00:26:39,280
All of it.

652
00:26:41,600 --> 00:26:41,920
OK.

653
00:26:41,920 --> 00:26:42,600
That's enough.

654
00:26:47,000 --> 00:26:49,120
The dinner is accomplished.

655
00:26:49,760 --> 00:26:51,440
We can start eating.

656
00:26:51,440 --> 00:26:52,160
Where's the rice?

657
00:26:58,200 --> 00:26:59,800
I forgot to turn the rice cooker on.

658
00:27:05,440 --> 00:27:06,880
May I speak to the person in charge?

659
00:27:09,160 --> 00:27:10,240
Who are you?

660
00:27:10,240 --> 00:27:12,360
We're from the Administration for Market Regulation.

661
00:27:14,000 --> 00:27:14,880
Just a moment.

662
00:27:14,880 --> 00:27:16,140
I will inform the manager for you.

663
00:27:16,140 --> 00:27:16,640
OK.

664
00:27:22,800 --> 00:27:23,760
Feng Xi.

665
00:27:24,130 --> 00:27:26,080
Don't forget the fire safety incident last time.

666
00:27:26,080 --> 00:27:26,800
Mind your attitude.

667
00:27:27,000 --> 00:27:27,520
I know.

668
00:27:31,640 --> 00:27:32,160
Hello.

669
00:27:32,160 --> 00:27:32,600
Hello.

670
00:27:32,600 --> 00:27:33,880
I'm the manager here.

671
00:27:34,360 --> 00:27:35,560
Get them two cups of water, Ding.

672
00:27:35,800 --> 00:27:36,440
OK.

673
00:27:37,160 --> 00:27:38,280
Sit, please.

674
00:27:38,480 --> 00:27:40,120
We're here because we received a report

675
00:27:40,440 --> 00:27:42,120
that you have food safety problems.

676
00:27:42,200 --> 00:27:42,800
Report?

677
00:27:43,560 --> 00:27:44,280
Who reported it?

678
00:27:44,280 --> 00:27:45,440
I'm afraid we can't tell you that.

679
00:27:45,880 --> 00:27:47,040
Here's the material.

680
00:27:47,080 --> 00:27:48,160
Please cooperate.

681
00:27:48,400 --> 00:27:48,960
I'm listening.

682
00:27:48,960 --> 00:27:49,920
What can we do to cooperate?

683
00:27:49,960 --> 00:27:51,440
You have a dish called

684
00:27:51,440 --> 00:27:53,120
Jerkies and Prawn Cake Sandwich.

685
00:27:53,120 --> 00:27:53,520
Right?

686
00:27:53,520 --> 00:27:54,000
Yes.

687
00:27:54,600 --> 00:27:55,840
Can you make one for me?

688
00:27:55,840 --> 00:27:57,440
We need to get into the kitchen.

689
00:27:58,920 --> 00:27:59,920
The jerkies we use are

690
00:27:59,920 --> 00:28:01,840
from Macao and shipped by air.

691
00:28:02,160 --> 00:28:03,880
The prawn cakes are made from fresh prawns.

692
00:28:15,320 --> 00:28:16,360
Put is down now.

693
00:28:20,520 --> 00:28:21,600
What's wrong?

694
00:28:21,600 --> 00:28:22,600
Give me the knife.

695
00:28:25,760 --> 00:28:28,400
You need to separate knives for raw 
 and cooked food, right?

696
00:28:28,400 --> 00:28:29,200
Yes.

697
00:28:29,640 --> 00:28:31,760
There're jerkies and prawn cakes in this sandwich.

698
00:28:31,760 --> 00:28:33,720
I also see lettuce and tomatoes, right?

699
00:28:33,720 --> 00:28:34,360
Yes.

700
00:28:34,360 --> 00:28:35,080
Let me ask you.

701
00:28:35,400 --> 00:28:38,320
Is this knife for raw or cooked food?

702
00:28:41,520 --> 00:28:43,360
Don't you separate raw and cooked food?

703
00:28:46,600 --> 00:28:48,000
But five-star hotels also

704
00:28:48,000 --> 00:28:49,600
cut their sandwiches in half from the middle.

705
00:28:49,600 --> 00:28:51,370
Are their knives for raw or cooked food?

706
00:28:51,370 --> 00:28:53,200
Even five-star hotels need to suspend business

707
00:28:53,200 --> 00:28:55,400
for rectification if they can't meet 
 hygiene standards.

708
00:28:55,640 --> 00:28:56,400
You are right.

709
00:28:56,400 --> 00:28:57,760
What do you think we need to do?

710
00:28:57,760 --> 00:28:58,480
We will cooperate.

711
00:28:58,560 --> 00:28:59,200
Let's talk outside.

712
00:28:59,680 --> 00:29:00,360
OK.

713
00:29:21,240 --> 00:29:22,760
If I wasn't at home during the weekend,

714
00:29:22,760 --> 00:29:23,920
where else can I be?

715
00:29:25,960 --> 00:29:27,920
Why have we been suspended again?

716
00:29:28,400 --> 00:29:29,520
What happened?

717
00:29:32,320 --> 00:29:33,120
Come on.

718
00:29:34,010 --> 00:29:35,800
Let's take this dish off the menu first.

719
00:29:35,800 --> 00:29:37,280
Don't get suspended because of this.

720
00:29:37,840 --> 00:29:38,400
Right.

721
00:29:38,400 --> 00:29:41,080
I invited people to have dinner there.

722
00:29:43,160 --> 00:29:45,440
We're not opening. Can't we just serve ourselves?

723
00:29:46,880 --> 00:29:47,560
Prepare the food.

724
00:29:52,600 --> 00:29:54,480
It's so troublesome.

725
00:29:59,120 --> 00:30:00,760
It's just an inspection.

726
00:30:00,760 --> 00:30:01,920
Why are you so worried?

727
00:30:02,340 --> 00:30:03,840
Take my place if you can manage.

728
00:30:03,840 --> 00:30:04,840
I can't.

729
00:30:04,840 --> 00:30:06,760
I have never written a self-criticism since young.

730
00:30:06,760 --> 00:30:08,040
You have the experience, at least.

731
00:30:08,800 --> 00:30:10,920
But last time, I wrote it for you.

732
00:30:11,240 --> 00:30:12,720
Still, you did it before.

733
00:30:12,720 --> 00:30:14,280
You must be more experienced than me.

734
00:30:19,800 --> 00:30:20,440
Come on.

735
00:30:21,120 --> 00:30:22,040
I'll give you an example.

736
00:30:23,440 --> 00:30:24,680
Distinguished leaders,

737
00:30:27,640 --> 00:30:30,760
We know the seriousness of our mistakes.

738
00:30:32,040 --> 00:30:34,960
Before coming up with a solution,

739
00:30:34,960 --> 00:30:36,560
we will take this dish off the menu.

740
00:30:37,040 --> 00:30:38,040
In the future, we promise

741
00:30:38,040 --> 00:30:40,960
there will never be similar problems again.

742
00:30:41,080 --> 00:30:42,200
We also promise

743
00:30:42,400 --> 00:30:44,560
that we won't make the same mistake again.

744
00:30:46,120 --> 00:30:46,960
Sign it.

745
00:30:46,960 --> 00:30:48,480
Best regards.

746
00:30:49,960 --> 00:30:51,440
Is that all?

747
00:30:51,440 --> 00:30:53,720
It's like primary school students making sentences.

748
00:30:54,520 --> 00:30:55,920
That's the same idea.

749
00:30:55,920 --> 00:30:57,360
Improvise a bit.

750
00:30:57,360 --> 00:30:59,160
If you can't do it, ask Henan for help.

751
00:31:02,440 --> 00:31:03,280
Where's Henan?

752
00:31:03,480 --> 00:31:05,240
He said he'll go out and think about a solution.

753
00:31:06,640 --> 00:31:08,120
If he can't do it inside the restaurant,

754
00:31:08,120 --> 00:31:09,640
why does he think he can do it outside?

755
00:31:10,360 --> 00:31:11,920
We can't always be suspended.

756
00:31:11,920 --> 00:31:12,560
I mean it.

757
00:31:13,120 --> 00:31:14,480
Let's just take it off the menu.

758
00:31:14,920 --> 00:31:16,080
You're not working in the restaurant.

759
00:31:16,080 --> 00:31:17,160
You don't know the situation.

760
00:31:17,680 --> 00:31:19,280
Do you have any idea how many of these

761
00:31:19,600 --> 00:31:20,800
sandwiches we sell each day

762
00:31:20,800 --> 00:31:22,120
for dine-in and takeaway?

763
00:31:22,440 --> 00:31:23,240
How many?

764
00:31:23,560 --> 00:31:24,800
At least 50.

765
00:31:24,920 --> 00:31:26,840
Our record is 102 orders in a day.

766
00:31:27,320 --> 00:31:28,480
The price is 38 RMB each.

767
00:31:28,640 --> 00:31:29,880
With this sandwich only,

768
00:31:29,920 --> 00:31:31,680
we can receive a few thousand RMB each day.

769
00:31:32,480 --> 00:31:33,640
Don't tell me to take it off.

770
00:31:34,280 --> 00:31:35,960
We can't do that, then.

771
00:31:37,280 --> 00:31:37,960
How about this?

772
00:31:39,800 --> 00:31:40,760
We serve it as a whole.

773
00:31:40,880 --> 00:31:42,240
Let's see which is the biggest.

774
00:31:43,440 --> 00:31:45,200
Stop being annoying.

775
00:31:45,600 --> 00:31:47,040
Let him think about it first.

776
00:31:47,040 --> 00:31:47,840
He can think about it.

777
00:31:47,840 --> 00:31:48,920
But you need to write it, too.

778
00:31:48,920 --> 00:31:50,200
Hand it in tomorrow.

779
00:31:50,360 --> 00:31:51,160
Pay the fine, too.

780
00:31:51,410 --> 00:31:53,000
We have to reopen tomorrow. Understood?

781
00:31:53,000 --> 00:31:54,040
Alright. Stop nagging.

782
00:31:55,560 --> 00:31:56,600
Me, nagging?

783
00:31:56,600 --> 00:31:58,000
Who called me in the morning,

784
00:31:58,000 --> 00:31:58,680
whimpering

785
00:31:58,680 --> 00:32:00,600
and said, "We're suspended again"?

786
00:32:09,600 --> 00:32:11,920
Tell me, have we crossed someone?

787
00:32:12,000 --> 00:32:13,120
You're so annoying.

788
00:32:13,120 --> 00:32:14,560
I just thought about something.

789
00:32:28,120 --> 00:32:29,160
Hi, Mr. Lu.

790
00:32:29,800 --> 00:32:30,640
Shanshan.

791
00:32:30,640 --> 00:32:31,880
Why are you alone?

792
00:32:32,240 --> 00:32:33,200
I arrived here first.

793
00:32:33,200 --> 00:32:34,400
My friends are on the way.

794
00:32:34,520 --> 00:32:35,920
Let's have an agreement.

795
00:32:35,920 --> 00:32:37,640
It's my treat today. Don't you ask for the bill!

796
00:32:37,640 --> 00:32:38,360
I can't agree.

797
00:32:38,720 --> 00:32:41,480
I come here for dinner to support you.

798
00:32:41,480 --> 00:32:42,760
I can't let you pay for dinner.

799
00:32:43,000 --> 00:32:44,080
To be honest,

800
00:32:44,120 --> 00:32:45,520
something went wrong in my restaurant.

801
00:32:45,520 --> 00:32:46,560
We're suspended from rectifying.

802
00:32:46,560 --> 00:32:48,240
If you pay, it counts as I'm opening for business.

803
00:32:48,240 --> 00:32:49,800
That would be my mistake.

804
00:32:49,800 --> 00:32:50,720
Next time.

805
00:32:50,720 --> 00:32:51,560
Next time.

806
00:32:51,960 --> 00:32:52,720
Alright.

807
00:32:53,000 --> 00:32:54,280
If you insist.

808
00:32:54,480 --> 00:32:55,130
Sit here.

809
00:32:55,130 --> 00:32:56,280
I'll arrange the dishes for you.

810
00:32:56,280 --> 00:32:57,000
Alright.

811
00:32:57,400 --> 00:33:00,720
[Crossroad Bistro]

812
00:33:13,960 --> 00:33:16,240
What do you think this knife is for, raw or cooked?

813
00:33:18,160 --> 00:33:19,800
A disposable knife.

814
00:33:22,160 --> 00:33:23,480
Why are you so clever?

815
00:33:28,520 --> 00:33:29,320
Not bad.

816
00:33:29,920 --> 00:33:30,600
Very deep.

817
00:33:30,840 --> 00:33:32,560
Also, you have literary talent.

818
00:33:33,280 --> 00:33:34,200
I'm not as talented as you.

819
00:33:34,640 --> 00:33:35,400
I'm not talented at all.

820
00:33:35,640 --> 00:33:36,400
These are

821
00:33:37,640 --> 00:33:38,680
just lousy ideas.

822
00:33:44,240 --> 00:33:44,840
Why do I feel

823
00:33:44,840 --> 00:33:46,560
this sandwich is so tasty today?

824
00:33:48,120 --> 00:33:49,960
You have solved two difficult problems for me.

825
00:33:49,960 --> 00:33:50,840
What can I do to thank you?

826
00:33:54,080 --> 00:33:55,000
Don't thank me.

827
00:33:55,640 --> 00:33:56,320
How about

828
00:33:57,280 --> 00:33:58,360
you help me out?

829
00:33:58,760 --> 00:33:59,400
Tell me.

830
00:34:02,600 --> 00:34:03,480
My parents

831
00:34:03,480 --> 00:34:04,960
always urge me to find a girlfriend.

832
00:34:05,880 --> 00:34:07,280
You know what my mom is like.

833
00:34:07,480 --> 00:34:09,600
Once in a while, she asks others to introduce girls to me.

834
00:34:09,600 --> 00:34:11,000
She also insists that I should meet them.

835
00:34:11,000 --> 00:34:13,010
To meet some of them, I even had to go back to my hometown.

836
00:34:13,010 --> 00:34:15,400
I just paid lip service and said I already 
 have a girlfriend.

837
00:34:16,280 --> 00:34:16,840
Then?

838
00:34:17,199 --> 00:34:18,520
Autumn is coming.

839
00:34:18,520 --> 00:34:20,320
They said when the weather cools down,

840
00:34:20,320 --> 00:34:21,679
they will come to Beijing and visit me.

841
00:34:21,679 --> 00:34:23,560
If I find a girlfriend

842
00:34:23,560 --> 00:34:25,000
before they come and visit,

843
00:34:25,000 --> 00:34:25,980
don't worry about it.

844
00:34:26,920 --> 00:34:28,880
If I didn't, can I ask you to...

845
00:34:33,440 --> 00:34:35,000
To what?

846
00:34:43,520 --> 00:34:45,480
Can I ask you to tell Sun

847
00:34:45,560 --> 00:34:46,320
and persuade her?

848
00:34:46,320 --> 00:34:48,080
Ask her to pretend to be my girlfriend.

849
00:34:50,199 --> 00:34:51,760
Do you want to piss your mom off to death

850
00:34:52,280 --> 00:34:54,280
or do you want to be beaten to death by Sun's husband?

851
00:35:04,880 --> 00:35:05,400
Hello.

852
00:35:05,520 --> 00:35:06,200
Hello.

853
00:35:06,240 --> 00:35:07,000
Two guests?

854
00:35:07,000 --> 00:35:07,480
Yes.

855
00:35:08,400 --> 00:35:08,920
Girl,

856
00:35:09,400 --> 00:35:10,960
you're Feng Xi, right?

857
00:35:11,040 --> 00:35:11,680
Yes.

858
00:35:11,680 --> 00:35:12,560
Who are you?

859
00:35:12,560 --> 00:35:14,400
We're Zhao Henan's parents.

860
00:35:15,080 --> 00:35:16,320
Hello, uncle and aunt.

861
00:35:16,320 --> 00:35:17,120
Come in, please.

862
00:35:17,360 --> 00:35:18,360
Your parents are here.

863
00:35:18,360 --> 00:35:19,200
My parents?

864
00:35:19,640 --> 00:35:20,840
Don't forget what I told you.

865
00:35:22,000 --> 00:35:23,160
I won't.

866
00:35:23,200 --> 00:35:24,640
